---
description: Bundle builder, transaction sender, and signer safety
globs:
  - "crates/builder/src/**/*.rs"
  - "crates/signer/src/**/*.rs"
  - "bin/rundler/src/cli/builder.rs"
  - "bin/rundler/src/cli/signer.rs"
---

- Keep sender errors distinct; fallback should activate only for `SenderUnavailable`.
- Return signer leases on every completion, failure, cancellation, and early-exit path.
- Store private keys, mnemonics, Flashbots auth, and Bloxroute auth in `SecretString`.
- Preserve Redis-backed KMS locking semantics when multiple KMS keys are configured.
- Match mempool filters with builder affinity or filtered operations may never be bundled.

Full details: `.agents/skills/builder-signer/`.
